body.description: Little fashionistas know that Minnie Mouse has a style of her own. With the Disney Junior Minnie Mouse Glitter and Glam Pet Fashion set, kids can dress Minnie Mouse and her puppy Cream Puff in matching outfits and bow-tastic accessories! This 25-piece doll and accessories set comes with a 6-inch poseable Minnie Mouse doll with 5 fabulous outfits and a Cream Puff figure with 4 outfits to coordinate with Minnie's. Made to mix and match, the colorful fashions and accessories are easy to put on and take off, so little ones can improve their coordination and confidence while expressing their personal style. Dress Minnie Mouse to go out on the town with adorable Cream Puff by her side! For more mix-and-match styling fun, look for the Disney Junior Minnie Mouse Fabulous Fashion Dolls and accessories (each sold separately) from Just Play. For kids ages 3 years and up.
